WEBVTT Offset: 2.823

00:22.588 --> 00:28.235
Tori no saezuri de mezamemasu
<lang en>I wake up to the birds singing
<lang ja>鳥のさえずりで目覚めます

00:28.235 --> 00:33.882
Kyō wa jibun ga yaruki ga derudarou ka?
<lang en>Will I get motivation today?
<lang ja>今日は自分がやるきができるだろうか?

00:33.882 --> 00:39.441
Koppu ipai no mizu, gozaimasu
<lang en>Good morning, glass of water
<lang ja>コップ1杯の水,ございます

00:39.441 --> 00:45.176
Sekai wa mada sakasama no yōda
<lang en>The world still seems upside down
<lang ja>世界はまだ逆さまのようだ

01:07.765 --> 01:13.412
Darekaga inunosanpo oshite iru no mita
<lang en>I saw someone walking their dog
<lang ja>誰かが犬の散歩おしているの見た

01:13.412 --> 01:19.059
Dakara watashi wa inu ni yasashiku aisatsu shita
<lang en>So I kindly greeted the dog
<lang ja>だからワタシ和犬に優しく挨拶した

01:19.059 --> 01:24.706
Kyō no watashi no fukusō wa kawaīdesu ka?
<lang en>Does my outfit look cute today?
<lang ja>今日の私の服装はかわいいですか？

01:24.706 --> 01:30.353
Hontōni isshōkenmei ganbarimashita
<lang en>I worked really hard on it
<lang ja>本当に一生懸命頑張りました